00:03:13.480 --> 00:03:16.640
There's no way I can take linear
combinations of this

00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:19.390
guy and make the second
entry equal a 1 here.

00:03:19.390 --> 00:03:21.670
And likewise there's no way I
can take linear combinations

00:03:21.670 --> 00:03:24.480
of this guy and make this third
entry equal a 1 here.

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:27.390
So these are also
a basis for v.

